"Transform this research document/analysis into an interactive, single-page HTML report with the following specifications:

**STRUCTURE:**
- Fixed navigation sidebar with smooth scroll-to-section
- Hero section with key metrics visualization
- Content divided into 7-8 thematic sections
- Each section has: title, summary cards, and insight callouts
- Footer with attribution

**DESIGN:**
- Use Tailwind CSS via CDN for styling
- Color scheme: teal/blue primary, with semantic colors (red for warnings, green for insights)
- Typography: serif headings (Tiempos), sans-serif body (Inter)
- Responsive: collapsible sidebar on mobile
- Interactive: hover effects, smooth scrolling, mobile menu toggle

**FUNCTIONALITY:**
- Mobile sidebar toggle with click-outside-to-close
- Anchor link smooth scrolling
- Section dividers with gradients
- Code blocks for technical specifications
- Alert boxes for critical warnings

**CONTENT ORGANIZATION:**
Map each major research point to a card or list item. Use icons (Font Awesome) for visual markers. Ensure all citations are preserved as clickable links."
